{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistrationFailure:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:"}]},"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Handles push notification registration failure.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","text":"NSError"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The NSError received from APNs registration failure"}]}],"name":"error"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s "},{"code":"application:didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to notify Pushwoosh about registration failures.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This allows Pushwoosh to:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Log the error for debugging","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Retry registration if appropriate"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Update device status in the Control Panel","type":"text"}]}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"text":"Example","anchor":"Example","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle registration failure with user feedback:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didFailToRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithError error: Error) {","","        \/\/ Forward to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistrationFailure(error as NSError)","","        \/\/ Log for debugging","        Logger.error(\"Push registration failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","","        \/\/ Handle specific error cases","        let nsError = error as NSError","        switch nsError.code {","        case 3010:","            \/\/ Simulator or push not supported","            Logger.warning(\"Push notifications not supported on this device\")","","        default:","            \/\/ Track error in analytics","            Analytics.track(\"push_registration_failed\", properties: [","                \"error_code\": nsError.code,","                \"error_message\": nsError.localizedDescription","            ])","","            \/\/ Optionally notify user","            if shouldShowPushError {","                showPushRegistrationError()","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/handlePushRegistrationFailure:":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistrationFailure:","title":"handlePushRegistrationFailure:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Handles push notification registration failure."}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistrationfailure:","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"}}}